INDEX_HL=Stockholm Open - International Pinball Tournament
INDEX_MAIN=The Stockholm Open International Pinball Tournament was held at the Royal Institute of Technology (Kungliga Tekniska Högskolan, KTH) in Stockholm, Sweden on April 6-8, 2007. The date for 2008 has not yet been determined. The tournament is open to anyone who wishes to attend, and there are no special requirements for skill or citizenship to participate.<br /><br />The Stockholm Open started in 2004, and was an immediate success. It has grown to be one of the major pinball tournaments in the world, with participants from many different countries on several continents. 

